	   <tr><td colspan=2>The King and Shaman can be taken together with relative ease by 4 level 20's certainly.&nbsp;&nbsp;The best way to kill these two is as follows:<br>   1 - Clear the room...mana conservation is key  for casters, as spawn times are faitly short in this room, and you'll need to take out the King as quickly as you can once the room is clear.<br><br>   2 - If a necro or mage pet is available, have them attack the High Shaman.  This will draw the King's HT, and at level 20 my necro pet was usually able to fight the shammy alone until we finished the king.<br><br>   3 - Once the King HTs the pet, attack and kill first the king, then the shammy, then the king's pet if its still running around<br><br>Hope this helps.  I've accomplished this many times, primarily with groups of 4, levels 18-22 normally.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Basskix<br>Necromancer/Bertoxxulous server</td></tr>
